<TITLE> Satyam says business environment challenging </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 BANGALORE, Oct 17 (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - Satyam Computer Services Ltd said on Friday the near-term business environment was challenging amid the global economic slowdown and turmoil in the financial sector. "Consolidation among financial services companies is also contributing to uncertainty, although it is also creating transformational opportunities," Satyam Chairman B. Ramalinga Raju said in a statement. India's fourth-largest software services exporter reported a 42 percent jump in quarterly net profit, beating expectations, but cut its full-year revenue guidance in dollar terms
